==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Homesteader
<hw>Home"stead*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who has
entered upon a portion of the public land with the purpose of acquiring
ownership of it under provisions of the homestead law, so called; one
who has acquired a homestead in this manner.</def> <mark>[Local,
U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>homestretch</ent>⟦br⟧
